refs.lootbox_info: Each lootbox contains random reward, TON coins, USDT or game points.
refs.lootbox_info1: You can send it to your friend in Telegram, so when he will join game, both of you will receive some gift.

boosts.title: Boosters
boosts.autobot.description1: Autobot starts earning coins for you when you invite friends, they join the game and start earning coins. More friends you invite more coins autobot earns!

tasks.loginEveryDay: Login every day to claim your rewards!

swap.step1.label: Do you need referral?
swap.step1.desc: We will bring you a referral in exchange for you becoming a referral for two other people. You need to click on 2 links and start the game.
swap.step2.desc: Enter the link for which you need a referral
swap.step3.label: To get a referral, please complete a task from us!

swap.step4.label: Make sure you follow the links and started the bot.

swap.if_not_sure: If not sure, get back to previous screen.
